 Galvatron felt the pressure come down on him. He was almost completly 
flattened to the floor. He had his computer in his head calculate. !0 times 
normal gravity. "A good start. Now what he had to work was being able to move 
freely without any diffrence. Makeing his speed 10 times greater then it 
already was. He took steps. Loud thuds hitting the steel floor. He started to 
pace around the room. His traing for right now was a brisk walk in 10 times 
gravity and it took all the strength he had just to life his legs.
